        <h3>Advanced Analytics</h3>
        <p>Visual dashboards with usage patterns, yield predictions, and actionable insights for better decision-making.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card feature-card">
        <i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i>
        <h3>Billing & Invoicing</h3>
        <p>Automated, error-free billing and GST-ready invoicing to streamline sales and accounting processes.</p>
