          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">"The billing feature saves me hours every week. Now I can focus more on my crops rather than paperwork. Highly recommended for all farmers!"</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
